social_posts.post_text:
Counting down the days to @hotrodrockrumble! This year you’ll have more chances to catch our show, we’re performing every night! 5 shows jam packed with sideshow shenanigans! 

Love this pic from last year at the car show by @jeffgrayart

💛 I have so very few photos of my papa & me together, five, maybe six. He was killed when I was just 11 years old & most of the photos I had of him were lost in a CA wildfire….So imagine my surprise when I recently unpacked an old box and found this little treasure tucked away inside the folds of a book, a photo of us together that I’ve never seen before! After 30 years of hiding away in a dusty box this felt like a little piece of magic, like he was reaching out & giving me a great big hug when I needed it most. He always had a way of making everyone around him smile, and filling each day with joy. Even now he still finds a way. 💗 
Love you always dad.

Mr Donny Vomit & Frankie Sin | Whole Plate + Half Plate Tintypes 
.
.
.
It was such an honor getting to work with these two not only once but twice at the @hotrodrockrumble! They were a dream to work with and inspired me to take my tintype show on the road (aka living the dream)

Give this talented and amazing sideshow duo a follow so you’ll know when they’re in your city! You’ll definitely want to see @officiallyfrankie throw her knives! 

Thank you both for stopping by and I can’t wait to see y’all when you’re passing through Colorado again. 

For you Wet Platers: The first plate (whole) is an older silver bath with Tuti Fruity collodion. The second plate (half) is a fresh bath with fresh collodion.
